SPECIAL NOTICE: BitDip is an open source web development project in it's very early stages. Jim Bursch is the lead developer and he can be found on GitHub: https://github.com/jimbursch.

What is Bitcoin?
Bitcoin is a digital currency/money.

What is Diplomacy?
Diplomacy is a simple yet sophisticated game of grand strategy.

What is Bitcoin Diplomacy?
Bitcoin Diplomacy is an online version of the game Diplomacy (forked from webDiplomacy.net) combined with a system of finance denominated in Bitcoin. Essentially, at BitDip you play Diplomacy for real money.
